---
import SectionHeader from "../ui/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section about">
  <div class="container-page">
    <SectionHeader id="about" eyebrow="brief background" count={1} />

    <div class="about__grid">
      <div class="about__prose">
        <p class="scroll-reveal-text">
          I'm an Engineering Manager at
          <svg class="inline-mark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path
              d="M7 4 L17 12 L7 20"
              stroke="#65A637"
              stroke-width="3.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              fill="none"
            />
          </svg>Splunk, leading the team that owns identity, access, and
          integrations for Splunk Observability Cloud. I've been at Splunk
          seven years across IC and EM roles &mdash; long enough to ship
          Unified Identity end-to-end, build a custom RBAC system from
          scratch, and promote four engineers along the way.
        </p>
        <p class="scroll-reveal-text">
          Outside of work: roughly 6,000 hours of
          <svg class="inline-mark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="3" fill="#0E0F0F"/>
            <path
              d="M7 17 L12 6 L17 17 Z M9.4 13.4 H14.6"
              stroke="#C70206"
              stroke-width="1.6"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              fill="none"
            />
          </svg>Dota 2 across the years, 100,000+
          <svg class="inline-mark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="11" fill="#1DB954"/>
            <path d="M6.2 14.6 Q12 12 17.8 14.6"  stroke="#0E0F0F" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M7.2 11.6 Q12 9.4 16.8 11.6" stroke="#0E0F0F" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M8.2 8.8  Q12 7   15.8 8.8"  stroke="#0E0F0F" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>Spotify minutes a year, ten-plus
          <span class="inline-mark inline-mark--emoji" aria-hidden="true">🎸</span>concerts
          when the calendar allows, and an
          <svg class="inline-mark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10.4" stroke="#FA114F" stroke-width="2.4" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="7.0"  stroke="#92E82A" stroke-width="2.4" fill="none"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.6"  stroke="#1EEAEF" stroke-width="2.4" fill="none"/>
          </svg>Apple Watch I'm forever trying to close out before midnight.
        </p>
        <p class="scroll-reveal-text">
          The throughline, if there is one, is that I keep ending up at the
          seam between platforms &mdash; wiring things together that weren't
          designed to talk to each other, then figuring out who's allowed to
          do what once they can.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about__sidebar" aria-label="quick facts">
        <dl class="about__facts">
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-mono-sm">based in</dt>
            <dd>San Francisco Bay Area</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-mono-sm">currently</dt>
            <dd>Engineering Manager · Splunk</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-mono-sm">scope</dt>
            <dd>AI, Identity, Integrations</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-mono text-mono-sm">open to</dt>
            <dd>EM · PM · Staff Eng at AI labs &amp; product cos</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
  }
  @media (min-width: 880px) {
    .about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(220px, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .about__prose {
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }
  .about__prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.2vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1.4em 0;
  }
  .about__prose code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-bg-elev);
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .about__sidebar {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-left: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .about__sidebar {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    }
  }
  .about__facts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .about__facts > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .about__facts dt {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-transform: lowercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .about__facts dd {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
